entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Corellia system and follow the route waypoints. Station command has been asked to assist you by updating the waypoints along your route as needed.
entries.quest_patrol1_d: We've been asked to assist you. First set course for the first waypoint. You will be backtracking along the approach that the transport would have taken to the space station.
entries.quest_patrol2_d: Head towards the second waypoint set to your Nav computer. Nothing out of the ordinary as yet.
entries.quest_patrol3_d: Now move on to the third watpoint along the transport's route.
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a route waypoint, Station Command will update your nav computer with the next one.
entries.split_quest_alert: Incoming unidentified fighers with active weapon systems. Wait... they appear to be Ragtag fighters. What could they want?
entries.title: Corellia System: Trace the Delivery Transport's Route
entries.title_d: Trace the route into the Corellia system that the transport scheduled to deliver Ral's shipment would have taken. You will be backtracking along that route in reverse order from the station.
